{"data":[{"date":"18:29 16/06","title":"Nh\u1eefng d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n v\u00e0ng cho tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u c\u00e2n s\u1ee9c Peru vs \u0110an M\u1ea1ch","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/15/nhung-nhan-dinh-peru-vs-dan-mach-va-du-doan-peru-vs-dan-mach.png","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp Croatia vs Nigeria: C\u1eadp nh\u1eadt li\u00ean t\u1ee5c di\u1ec5n bi\u1ebfn t\u01b0\u1eddng thu\u1eadt t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Croatia vs Nigeria b\u1ea3ng D World Cup 2018 l\u00fac 02h00 \u0111\u00eam ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m nay 17/6.</h2><h2>Tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp Croatia vs Nigeria: C\u1eadp nh\u1eadt li\u00ean t\u1ee5c di\u1ec5n bi\u1ebfn t\u01b0\u1eddng thu\u1eadt t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Croatia vs Nigeria b\u1ea3ng D World Cup 2018 l\u00fac 02h00 \u0111\u00eam ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m nay 17/6.</h2>\r\nB\u1ecb l\u1ed7i, vui l\u00f2ng click v\u00e0o \u0111\u00e2y <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/truc-tiep-world-cup-2018/tran-dau/croatia-vs-nigeria-bang-d-463-188655.html\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgb(128, 0, 0);\"><u><strong>TR\u1ef0C TI\u1ebeP CROATIA VS NIGERIA</strong></u></span></span></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"241","checkdouble":"188650"},{"date":"18:25 16/06","title":"T\u1ea3n m\u1ea1n World Cup: T\u1eeb tr\u1eadn Maroc 0-1 Iran ngh\u0129 v\u1ec1 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/16/tan-man-world-cup-tu-tran-maroc-01-iran-nghi-ve-bong-da-viet-nam.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Trong m\u1ed9t th\u1ebf tr\u1eadn b\u1ecb \u00e9p s\u00e2n to\u00e0n di\u1ec7n, \u0110T Iran v\u1eabn may m\u1eafn c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng \u0111\u1ea7u tay t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018. V\u00e0 nh\u00ecn v\u00e0o nh\u1eefng g\u00ec \u0111\u00e3 di\u1ec5n ra, r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam v\u1eabn c\u00f2n r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u vi\u1ec7c ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0m tr\u00ean h\u00e0nh tr\u00ecnh v\u01b0\u01a1n ra th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi.</h2><h2>Iran may m\u1eafn c\u00f3 th\u1eafng l\u1ee3i th\u1ee9 hai \u1edf World Cup</h2>\r\n<h2><o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u1ed1i ng\u00e0y 15/6, \u0110T Iran c\u00f3 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018 v\u00e0 c\u0169ng l\u00e0 l\u1ea7n th\u1ee9 5 h\u1ecd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u1edf \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u01b0\u1eddng th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi. Trong 4 l\u1ea7n tham d\u1ef1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3, th\u00e0nh t\u00edch c\u1ee7a n\u1ec1n b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u ch\u00e2u l\u1ee5c ph\u1ea3i n\u00f3i l\u00e0 h\u1ebft s\u1ee9c th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong l\u1ecbch s\u1eed, \u0110T Iran ch\u01b0a t\u1eebng v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng trong nh\u1eefng l\u1ea7n tham d\u1ef1 s\u00e2n ch\u01a1i l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t h\u00e0nh tinh. H\u1ecd \u0111\u1ec3 thua 8, h\u00f2a 3 v\u00e0 m\u1edbi ch\u1ec9 th\u1eafng duy nh\u1ea5t \u0111\u00fang 1 tr\u1eadn. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 2-1 c\u1ee7a Iran tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n M\u1ef9 \u1edf k\u1ef3 World Cup di\u1ec5n ra v\u00e0o n\u0103m 1998 tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea5t Ph\u00e1p.&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">20 n\u0103m cho nh\u1eefng s\u1ef1 n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c v\u00e0 quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m, cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng v\u1eadn may c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 m\u1ec9m c\u01b0\u1eddi v\u1edbi ng\u01b0\u1eddi Iran khi h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng th\u1ee9 hai \u1edf \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u01b0\u1eddng th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi. Ch\u01a1i l\u00e9p v\u1ebf to\u00e0n di\u1ec7n tr\u01b0\u1edbc Ma-r\u1ed1c song chung cu\u1ed9c, Iran l\u1ea1i gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng&nbsp;<strong><span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/truc-tiep-world-cup-2018/tran-dau/maroc-vs-iran-bang-b-463-188560.html\" target=\"_blank\">1-0</span>&nbsp;</strong>v\u1edbi m\u00f3n qu\u00e0 t\u1eeb tr\u00ean tr\u1eddi r\u01a1i xu\u1ed1ng khi c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a Maroc, Aziz Bouhaddouz \u0111\u1ed1t l\u01b0\u1edbi nh\u00e0 \u1edf ph\u00fat 90+5.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"T\u1eeb tr\u1eadn Maroc 0-1 \u0110T Iran ngh\u0129 v\u1ec1 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"T\u1eeb tr\u1eadn Maroc 0-1 \u0110T Iran ngh\u0129 v\u1ec1 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/16/Tu-tran-Maroc-0-1-DT-Iran-nghi-ve-bong-da-Viet-Nam-hinh-anh.png\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>\u0110T Iran may m\u1eafn c\u00f3 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng th\u1ee9 hai t\u1ea1i World Cup</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u01b0\u1edbc b\u00e0n th\u1eafng \u0111\u00f3, c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 n\u00f3i ng\u01b0\u1eddi Iran \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ea3i thi \u0111\u1ea5u v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng ch\u1eadt v\u1eadt tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u1ed9t Maroc h\u01a1n h\u1eb3n v\u1ec1 s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh, t\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9 v\u00e0 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u1ea7m b\u00f3ng. Iran g\u1ea7n nh\u01b0 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 tri\u1ec3n khai c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ee3t t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng m\u00e0 ch\u1ec9 ch\u1ed1ng tr\u1ea3 y\u1ebfu \u1edbt, khi\u1ebfn th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh Beiranvand ph\u1ea3i li\u00ean t\u1ee5c ph\u1ea3i c\u1ee9u thua tr\u01b0\u1edbc s\u1ee9c \u00e9p r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u1ebfn t\u1eeb ch\u00e2u Phi.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong 15 ph\u00fat \u0111\u1ea7u tr\u1eadn, \u0110T Maroc li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp t\u1ea1o ra nh\u1eefng t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng nguy hi\u1ec1m tr\u01b0\u1edbc khung th\u00e0nh c\u1ee7a Iran. \u0110\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a ch\u00e2u Phi ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n l\u00e0m ch\u1ee7 cu\u1ed9c ch\u01a1i v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ea9y c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u00e1o tr\u1eafng v\u00e0o th\u1ebf b\u1ecb \u0111\u1ed9ng. Tuy nhi\u00ean s\u1ef1 l\u0103n x\u1ea3 c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng t\u1eebng 3 l\u1ea7n v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch ch\u00e2u \u00c1 gi\u00fap h\u1ecd c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ee9ng v\u1eefng tr\u01b0\u1edbc nh\u1eefng l\u00e0n s\u00f3ng t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng ph\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ea7u c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nh\u00ecn v\u00e0o s\u1ef1 n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c c\u1ee7a Iran m\u1edbi th\u1ea5y chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 r\u1ea5t \u00fd ngh\u0129a. 4 n\u0103m tr\u01b0\u1edbc t\u1ea1i Brazil, gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t h\u00e0nh tinh th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t n\u1ed7i h\u1ed5 th\u1eb9n d\u00e0nh cho c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ebfn t\u1eeb ch\u00e2u \u00c1 khi m\u00e0 c\u1ea3 Iran, Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n, H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c v\u00e0 Australia ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 gi\u00e0nh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ed1 \u0111i\u1ec3m \u0111\u00fang b\u1eb1ng m\u1ed9t chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng trong t\u1ed5ng s\u1ed1 12 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u1edf World Cup.&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">N\u00f3 cho th\u1ea5y kho\u1ea3ng c\u00e1ch gi\u1eefa b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00e2u \u00c1 v\u1edbi c\u00e1c l\u1ee5c \u0111\u1ecba kh\u00e1c v\u1eabn c\u00f2n m\u1ed9t kho\u1ea3ng c\u00e1ch r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn. D\u1eabu sao th\u1eafng l\u1ee3i c\u1ee7a th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Carlos Queiroz c\u0169ng l\u00e0 ngu\u1ed3n c\u1ed5 v\u0169 \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a ch\u00e2u l\u1ee5c c\u00f3 th\u00eam \u0111\u1ed9ng l\u1ef1c \u0111\u1ec3 h\u01b0\u1edbng t\u1edbi nh\u1eefng k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 t\u1ed1t trong nh\u1eefng tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1edbi, d\u00f9 v\u1eabn bi\u1ebft c\u1eeda \u0111i ti\u1ebfp c\u1ee7a c\u1ea3 Iran, Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n, H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c, Australia v\u00e0 Saudi Arabia \u1edf k\u1ef3 World Cup n\u0103m nay \u0111\u1ec1u l\u00e0 r\u1ea5t th\u1ea5p.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/nhung-diem-nhan-sau-tran-thua-soc-cua-ma-roc-truoc-iran-421-188588.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/16/nhung-diem-nhan-sau-tran-thua-soc-cua-ma-roc-truoc-iran.JPG\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/nhung-diem-nhan-sau-tran-thua-soc-cua-ma-roc-truoc-iran-421-188588.html\">Nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec3m nh\u1ea5n sau tr\u1eadn thua s\u1ed1c c\u1ee7a Ma R\u1ed1c tr\u01b0\u1edbc Iran</span><br>\r\nMa R\u1ed1c d\u00f9 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao h\u01a1n Iran nh\u01b0ng l\u1ea1i g\u00e2y th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng khi \u0111\u1ec3 thua v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 t\u1ed1i thi\u1ec3u, c\u00f9ng \u0111i\u1ec3m qua nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec3m nh\u1ea5n sau tr\u1eadn Ma R\u1ed1c vs Iran b\u1ea3ng B...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam v\u1eabn \u1edf m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p r\u1ea5t xa World Cup<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ch\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn n\u1ec1n b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u ch\u00e2u \u00c1 nh\u01b0 Iran tr\u1ea3i qua m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ea7y ch\u1eadt v\u1eadt tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 t\u00ean tu\u1ed5i tr\u00ean b\u1ea3n \u0111\u1ed3 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi nh\u01b0 Maroc m\u1edbi th\u1ea5y tr\u00ecnh \u0111\u1ed9 c\u1ee7a b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam c\u00f2n h\u1ea1n ch\u1ebf th\u1ebf n\u00e0o.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">R\u00f5 r\u00e0ng thay v\u00ec ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c m\u01a1 m\u1ed9ng v\u1edbi vi\u1ec5n c\u1ea3nh d\u1ef1 Wolrd Cup trong t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai, tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u1eaft m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau hi\u1ec7n h\u1eefu h\u01a1n c\u1ee7a \u0110T Vi\u1ec7t Nam s\u1ebd ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 thi \u0111\u1ea5u hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 v\u00e0 c\u00f3 \u0111i\u1ec3m tr\u01b0\u1edbc ch\u00ednh Iran, \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 m\u00e0 ch\u00fang ta s\u1ebd \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u t\u1ea1i VCK Asian Cup 2019.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Park Hang Seo DT Viet Nam\" title=\"HLV Park Hang Seo \u0110T Vi\u1ec7t Nam\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/16/park-hang-seo.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>Iran c\u0169ng ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 m\u00e0 \u0110T Vi\u1ec7t Nam s\u1ebd \u0111\u1ed1i m\u1eb7t t\u1ea1i VCK Asian Cup 2019</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u00e0o \u0111\u1ea7u th\u00e1ng 1 n\u0103m sau, \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Vi\u1ec7t Nam c\u1ee7a HLV Park Hang Seo s\u1ebd c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng m\u00e0n so t\u00e0i v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t ch\u00e2u l\u1ee5c t\u1ea1i VCK Asian Cup. V\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u00e1i t\u00ean trong s\u1ed1 \u0111\u00f3 ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 \u0110T Iran c\u1ee7a HLV Carlos Queiroz, nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111ang tham d\u1ef1 gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 s\u00f4i \u0111\u1ed9ng nh\u1ea5t h\u00e0nh tinh \u0111ang di\u1ec5n ra tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea5t Nga.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nh\u01b0 trung v\u1ec7 Qu\u1ebf Ng\u1ecdc H\u1ea3i \u0111\u00e3 n\u00f3i: &ldquo;7 th\u00e1ng n\u1eefa, n\u1ebfu Iran mang to\u00e0n b\u1ed9 \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh d\u1ef1 World Cup 2018 \u0111\u1ebfn ch\u1ea1m tr\u00e1n v\u1edbi tuy\u1ec3n Vi\u1ec7t Nam th\u00ec c\u1ea3m gi\u00e1c c\u00f3 l\u1ebd ph\u1ea5n kh\u00edch l\u1eafm!&rdquo;.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u00f3 ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn s\u1ebd l\u00e0 c\u1ea3m gi\u00e1c chung c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c tuy\u1ec3n th\u1ee7 Vi\u1ec7t Nam trong l\u1ea7n th\u1ee9 hai \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ti\u1ebfp c\u1eadn gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u ch\u00e2u l\u1ee5c. N\u1ebfu thi \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ed1t tr\u01b0\u1edbc Iran, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 l\u00e0 h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u ch\u00e2u \u00c1 v\u00e0 v\u1eeba tham d\u1ef1 World Cup, \u0111\u00f3 ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn s\u1ebd l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t k\u1ef7 ni\u1ec7m \u0111\u00e1ng nh\u1edb v\u1edbi \u0110T Vi\u1ec7t Nam. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Iran t\u1ea1i World Cup l\u1ea7n n\u00e0y \u0111ang c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 tr\u1ebb h\u00f3a l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng, v\u1edbi nhi\u1ec1u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 9X. Th\u1eadm ch\u00ed ng\u00f4i sao \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Iran l\u00e0 s\u1ed1 20, ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Sardar Azmoun c\u00f2n b\u1eb1ng tu\u1ed5i C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng. <br>\r\n<br>\r\nVi\u1ec7t Nam g\u1eb7p Iran \u0111\u00f3 ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn s\u1ebd l\u00e0 m\u00e0n \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u00ed c\u1ee7a s\u1ee9c tr\u1ebb, kinh nghi\u1ec7m v\u00e0 kh\u00e1t khao chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng, d\u00f9 Iran c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u00f3 s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh h\u01a1n h\u1eb3n.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u1ec3 ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c n\u1ed1i ti\u1ebfp th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng nh\u01b0 t\u1ea1i VCK U23 ch\u00e2u \u00c1, r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Park Hang Seo c\u00f2n r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u vi\u1ec7c ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0m, \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t l\u00e0 nhi\u1ec7m v\u1ee5 n\u00e2ng cao y\u1ebfu t\u1ed1 th\u1ec3 l\u1ef1c, v\u1ed1n v\u1eabn \u0111ang l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec3m y\u1ebfu c\u1ed1 h\u1eefu c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam n\u00f3i chung khi b\u01b0\u1edbc ra s\u00e2n ch\u01a1i ch\u00e2u l\u1ee5c.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nMinh Long (TTVN)<o:p></o:p></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"240","checkdouble":"188651"},{"date":"18:56 16/06","title":"T\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p: Ph\u00e1p 2-1 Australia (B\u1ea3ng C World Cup 2018)","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/16/tong-hop-phap-21-australia-bang-c-world-cup-2018.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>D\u00f9 g\u1eb7p nhi\u1ec1u kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n tr\u01b0\u1edbc Australia thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ea7y quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m, Les Bleus v\u1eabn c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng trong tr\u1eadn ra qu\u00e2n t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018. Pogba l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111em v\u1ec1 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m cho ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3, hai b\u00ean thi nhau ghi b\u00e0n t\u1eeb ch\u1ea5m 11m \u0111\u1ec1u nh\u1edd s\u1ef1 tr\u1ee3 gi\u00fap c\u1ee7a VAR.</h2><strong>B\u1ea3n quy\u1ec1n VTV</strong><br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>\u0110\u1ed8I H\u00ccNH THI \u0110\u1ea4U<br>\r\nPh\u00e1p:</strong> Lloris, Pavard, Varane, Umtiti, Hernandez, Kante, Pogba, Tolisso, Mbappe, Griezmann, Dembele<br>\r\n<strong>Australia:</strong> Ryan; Risdon, Milligan, Sainsbury, Behich; Jedinak, Mooy; Kruse, Leckie, Rogic; Nabbout <br>\r\n<br></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"239","checkdouble":"188652"},{"date":"20:23 16/06","title":"TR\u1ef0C TI\u1ebeP Croatia vs Nigeria 02h00 ng\u00e0y 17/6 (World Cup 2018)","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/15/croatia-vs-nigeria-bang-d.png","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp Croatia vs Nigeria: C\u1eadp nh\u1eadt li\u00ean t\u1ee5c di\u1ec5n bi\u1ebfn t\u01b0\u1eddng thu\u1eadt t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Croatia vs Nigeria b\u1ea3ng D World Cup 2018 l\u00fac 02h00 \u0111\u00eam ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m nay 17/6.</h2><h2>Tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp Croatia vs Nigeria: C\u1eadp nh\u1eadt li\u00ean t\u1ee5c di\u1ec5n bi\u1ebfn t\u01b0\u1eddng thu\u1eadt t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Croatia vs Nigeria b\u1ea3ng D World Cup 2018 l\u00fac 02h00 \u0111\u00eam ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m nay 17/6.</h2>\r\nB\u1ecb l\u1ed7i, vui l\u00f2ng click v\u00e0o \u0111\u00e2y <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/truc-tiep-world-cup-2018/tran-dau/croatia-vs-nigeria-bang-d-463-188655.html\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgb(128, 0, 0);\"><u><strong>TR\u1ef0C TI\u1ebeP CROATIA VS NIGERIA</strong></u></span></span></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"238","checkdouble":"188655"},{"date":"21:03 16/06","title":"Gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng v\u1ea5t v\u1ea3, Griezmann n\u00f3i g\u00ec","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/16/gianh-chien-thang-vat-va-griezmann-noi-gi.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Dider Deschamps \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ea7u su\u00f4n s\u1ebb tr\u1eadn ra qu\u00e2n, v\u00e0 d\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng g\u00ec Griezmann ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u sau tr\u1eadn Ph\u00e1p 2-1 Australia.\r\n</h2><h2>Griezmann kh\u00f4ng h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng v\u1ec1 m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao h\u01a1n h\u1eb3n \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7, tuy nhi\u00ean \u0110T Ph\u00e1p \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ea5t l\u1ef1c trong 45 ph\u00fat \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean. Th\u1eadm ch\u00ed h\u1ecd c\u0169ng ch\u1ec9 ghi b\u00e0n m\u1edf t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 t\u1eeb ch\u1ea5m ph\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ec1n, trong t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng hi\u1ebfm hoi s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng VAR, do c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a Antoine Griezmann.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong nh\u1eefng ph\u00fat c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i, h\u00e0ng ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 c\u1ee7a Ph\u00e1p m\u1eafc sai l\u1ea7m v\u1edbi t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng chuy\u1ec1n c\u1ee7a Umtiti, gi\u00fap Australia c\u00f3 b\u00e0n g\u1ee1 h\u00f2a. Trong nh\u1eefng ph\u00fat cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng, Paul Pogba may m\u1eafn ghi b\u00e0n, qua \u0111\u00f3 gi\u00fap G\u00e0 tr\u1ed1ng gi\u00e0nh 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m trong ng\u00e0y ra qu\u00e2n.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chia s\u1ebb v\u1ec1 k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 n\u00e0y, ch\u00e2n s\u00fat thu\u1ed9c bi\u00ean ch\u1ebf Atletico Madrid t\u1ecf ra kh\u00f4ng m\u1ea5y h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng. Griezmann cho bi\u1ebft: &ldquo;\u0110i\u1ec1u quan tr\u1ecdng nh\u1ea5t l\u00e0 s\u1ef1 th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a to\u00e0n \u0111\u1ed9i. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i v\u1eabn c\u00f2n r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u vi\u1ec7c ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0m, v\u00e0 s\u1ebd thi \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n \u1edf nh\u1eefng tr\u1eadn sau. M\u1ecdi th\u1ee9 kh\u00f4ng h\u1ec1 d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng, nh\u01b0ng ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ec3 chi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ea5u.&rdquo;<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Griezmann ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u sau tr\u1eadn Ph\u00e1p 2-1 Australia\" title=\"Griezmann ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u sau tr\u1eadn Ph\u00e1p 2-1 Australia\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/16/gianh-chien-thang-vat-va-griezmann-noi-gi.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Griezmann ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u sau tr\u1eadn Ph\u00e1p 2-1 Australia</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n&ldquo;\u0110i\u1ec1u c\u1ea7n thi\u1ebft l\u00e0 to\u00e0n \u0111\u1ed9i ph\u1ea3i t\u1eadp l\u00e0m quen v\u1edbi h\u1ec7 th\u1ed1ng, v\u00e0 t\u00ecm ra s\u1ef1 k\u1ebft n\u1ed1i v\u1edbi nhau. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i ph\u1ea3i th\u00edch nghi v\u1edbi b\u1ea7u kh\u00f4ng kh\u00ed, c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 \u00e1p l\u1ef1c \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n.&rdquo;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong khi \u0111\u00f3, ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111em v\u1ec1 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng cho G\u00e0 tr\u1ed1ng Gaulois &ndash; ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Paul Pogba t\u1ecf ra r\u1ea5t vui m\u1eebng: &ldquo;Th\u1eadt kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00e0nh 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m, nh\u01b0ng ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng b\u1ecf cu\u1ed9c. Gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u m\u1edf m\u00e0n l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t \u0111i\u1ec1u tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi.&rdquo;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;V\u1ec1 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng, t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 g\u1eb7p may m\u1eafn trong t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng \u0111\u00f3, khi h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00fap \u0111\u01b0a b\u00f3ng v\u00e0o l\u01b0\u1edbi. Tuy nhi\u00ean k\u1ec3 c\u1ea3 ghi b\u00e0n b\u1eb1ng tai, m\u0169i hay ch\u00e2n, kh\u00f4ng quan tr\u1ecdng, t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 \u0111\u1ec1u r\u1ea5t tuy\u1ec7t.&rdquo;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">B\u00ean c\u1ea1nh Pogba v\u00e0 Griezmann ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u sau tr\u1eadn <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/truc-tiep-world-cup-2018/tran-dau/phap-vs-australia-bang-c-463-188624.html\" target=\"_blank\">Ph\u00e1p 2-1 Australia</span>, &ldquo;t\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ed3&rdquo; Samuel Umtiti c\u0169ng b\u00e0y t\u1ecf s\u1ef1 h\u1ed1i ti\u1ebfc khi v\u00f4 t\u00ecnh \u0111\u1ec3 b\u00f3ng ch\u1ea1m tay. Trung v\u1ec7 Barca c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y r\u1ea5t vui khi c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u00e3 s\u1eeda sai gi\u00fap m\u00ecnh, qua \u0111\u00f3 gi\u00e0nh l\u1ea5y 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean ng\u00e0y ra qu\u00e2n.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Thong so tran dau Phap 2-1 Australia\" title=\"Th\u00f4ng s\u1ed1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Ph\u00e1p 2-1 Australia\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/16/Phap-2--Australia.png\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Th\u00f4ng s\u1ed1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Ph\u00e1p 2-1 Australia</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<h3>&nbsp;<img src=\"/Images/video-chi-tiet.jpg\" style=\"font-size: 12px; width: 300px; height: 220px;\" alt=\"\"></h3>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/video/tong-hop-phap-21-australia-bang-c-world-cup-2018-461-188652.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/16/tong-hop-phap-21-australia-bang-c-world-cup-2018.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/video/tong-hop-phap-21-australia-bang-c-world-cup-2018-461-188652.html\">T\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p: Ph\u00e1p 2-1 Australia (B\u1ea3ng C World Cup 2018)</span><br>\r\nD\u00f9 g\u1eb7p nhi\u1ec1u kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n tr\u01b0\u1edbc Australia thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ea7y quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m, Les Bleus v\u1eabn c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng trong tr\u1eadn ra qu\u00e2n t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018. Pogba l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111em v\u1ec1 3...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/ket-qua-phap-vs-australia-bang-c-hom-nay-421-188645.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/15/ket-qua-phap-vs-australia-bang-c-hom-nay.png\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/ket-qua-phap-vs-australia-bang-c-hom-nay-421-188645.html\">K\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 Ph\u00e1p vs Australia tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u b\u1ea3ng C World Cup 2018</span><br>\r\nChuy\u00ean trang Bongda24h c\u1eadp nh\u1eadt chi ti\u1ebft k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 Ph\u00e1p vs Australia tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u b\u1ea3ng C World Cup 2018 h\u00f4m nay. Th\u00f4ng tin k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3, t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1, ng\u01b0\u1eddi ghi b\u00e0n, di\u1ec5n bi\u1ebfn...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nguy\u1ec7t Anh (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"237","checkdouble":"188656"},{"date":"20:52 16/06","title":"T\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p: Argentina 1-1 Iceland (B\u1ea3ng D World Cup 2018)","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/16/20180616T142247Z_1464141538_RC16E5AC50B0_RTRMADP_3_SOCCERWORLDCUPARGICE.JPG","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Trong m\u1ed9t ng\u00e0y thi \u0111\u1ea5u v\u00f4 duy\u00ean, Messi c\u00f9ng c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ea3i ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 h\u00f2a trong tr\u1eadn ra qu\u00e2n t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018. Ch\u1eb3ng nh\u1eefng b\u1ecf l\u1ee1 h\u00e0ng lo\u1ea1t c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0103n b\u00e0n m\u00e0 ngay c\u1ea3 tr\u00ean ch\u1ea5m 11m, El Pulga c\u0169ng th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i.</h2><strong>B\u1ea3n quy\u1ec1n VTV</strong><br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u1ed8I H\u00ccNH THI \u0110\u1ea4U<br>\r\nArgentina: Willy Caballero; Nicolas Tagliafico, Nicolas Otamendi, Marcos Rojo, Eduardo Salvio; Javier Mascherano, Lucas Biglia; Maximiliano Meza, Lionel Messi, Angel Di Maria; Sergio Aguero.<br>\r\nIceland: Hannes Haldorsson; Kari Arnason, Birkir Mar Saevarsson, Ragnar Sigurdsson, Hordur Bjorgvin Magnusson; Johann Berg Gudmundsson, Aron Gunnarsson, Emil Hallfredsson; Bikir Bjarnason, Alfred Finnbogason, Gylfi Sigurdsson.\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/video/tong-hop-phap-21-australia-bang-c-world-cup-2018-461-188652.html\">T\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p: Ph\u00e1p 2-1 Australia (B\u1ea3ng C World Cup 2018)</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/video/tong-hop-nhung-cong-nghe-duoc-ap-dung-tai-world-cup-2018-461-188627.html\">T\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p nh\u1eefng c\u00f4ng ngh\u1ec7 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u00e1p d\u1ee5ng t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/video/tong-hop-bo-dao-nha-33-tay-ban-nha-bang-b-world-cup-2018-461-188595.html\">T\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p: B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha 3-3 T\u00e2y Ban Nha (B\u1ea3ng B World Cup 2018)</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/video/tong-hop-ai-cap-01-uruguay-bang-b-world-cup-2018-461-188579.html\">T\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p: Ai C\u1eadp 0-1 Uruguay (B\u1ea3ng B World Cup 2018)</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"236","checkdouble":"188657"},{"date":"22:31 16/06","title":"S\u1eafm vai ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00f9ng ng\u00e0y ra qu\u00e2n, Pogba nh\u1eadn t\u1edbi t\u1ea5p l\u1eddi khen","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/16/sam-vai-nguoi-hung-ngay-ra-quan-pogba-nhan-toi-tap-loi-khen.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i Didier Drogba \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao t\u1ea7m \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng c\u1ee7a ng\u00f4i sao Man Utd trong tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng Ph\u00e1p 2-1 Australia \u1edf b\u1ea3ng C World Cup 2018.</h2><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Tr\u00ean th\u1ef1c t\u1ebf, \u0111\u00e2y kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n t\u1ed5ng quan \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u01b0 k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng c\u1ee7a Paul Pogba c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 c\u1ea3 t\u1eadp th\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Ph\u00e1p. G\u00e0 Tr\u1ed1ng Gaulois thi \u0111\u1ea5u b\u1ebf t\u1eafc tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n Ch\u00e2u \u00c1 v\u1ed1n thua k\u00e9m v\u1ec1 m\u1ecdi m\u1eb7t, th\u1eadm ch\u00ed nhanh ch\u00f3ng b\u1ecb g\u1ee1 h\u00f2a sau khi Antoine Griezmann ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 m\u1edf t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 tr\u00ean ch\u1ea5m 11m.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Ph\u00e1p 2-1 Australia Ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00f9ng Pogba \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Ph\u00e1p 2-1 Australia Ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00f9ng Pogba \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/16/sam-vai-nguoi-hung-ngay-ra-quan-pogba-nhan-toi-tap-loi-khen.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Ng\u00f4i sao Paul Pogba ghi b\u00e0n quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh mang v\u1ec1 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng tr\u1eadn Ph\u00e1p 2-1 Australia</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">D\u1eabu sao, \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a Pogba v\u1eabn bi\u1ebft c\u00e1ch l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng \u0111\u00fang l\u00fac. B\u1ea5t ch\u1ea5p phong \u0111\u1ed9 m\u1edd nh\u1ea1t trong ph\u1ea7n l\u1edbn th\u1eddi gian \u1edf Kazan, ch\u00ednh anh v\u1eabn tung \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng ch\u1ecdc khe s\u1eafc s\u1ea3o cho Griezmann tho\u00e1t xu\u1ed1ng ki\u1ebfm penalty, v\u00e0 r\u1ed3i t\u1ef1 m\u00ecnh \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111o\u1ea1t chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng v\u1ea5t v\u1ea3 cho \u0111\u1ed9i nh\u00e0 v\u1edbi pha d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m trong t\u01b0 th\u1ebf v\u1edbi t\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u1ed1i may m\u1eafn.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">R\u00f5 r\u00e0ng, Pogba v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a th\u1ec3 thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c gi\u1edbi m\u1ed9 \u0111i\u1ec7u sau m\u1ed9t m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i \u1edf Man Utd. M\u1eb7c d\u00f9 v\u1eady, ng\u00f4i sao 25 tu\u1ed5i v\u1eabn nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u1eefng l\u1eddi ng\u1ee3i khen c\u1ee7a huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i Didier Drogba sau tr\u1eadn <span href=\"http://bongda24h.vn/truc-tiep-world-cup-2018/tran-dau/phap-vs-australia-bang-c-463-188624.html\" target=\"_blank\">Ph\u00e1p 2-1 Australia</span>. Ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u c\u1ee7a c\u1ef1u ch\u00e2n s\u00fat kh\u00e9t ti\u1ebfng c\u1ee7a Chelsea:<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/diem-nhan-phap-21-australia-421-188653.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/16/diem-nhan-phap-21-australia.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/diem-nhan-phap-21-australia-421-188653.html\">4 \u0111i\u1ec3m nh\u1ea5n r\u00fat ra t\u1eeb ng\u00e0y ra qu\u00e2n v\u1ea5t v\u1ea3 c\u1ee7a ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p</span><br>\r\nG\u00e0 Tr\u1ed1ng Gaulois kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ed9ng chi\u1ebfn d\u1ecbch c\u00fap v\u00e0ng h\u1ee9a h\u1eb9n tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea5t Nga c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh v\u1edbi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng tr\u01b0\u1edbc ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u00dac nh\u01b0ng r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng v\u1ea5t v\u1ea3 h\u01a1n d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn. T\u00ecm hi\u1ec3u nh\u1eefng...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">\u201cT\u00f4i th\u00ec ngh\u0129 r\u1eb1ng Pogba \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u hay v\u1edbi t\u1ea7m \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng l\u00ean l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i c\u1ee7a to\u00e0n \u0111\u1ed9i. C\u1eadu \u1ea5y kh\u00f4ng n\u1ed5i b\u1eadt hay b\u00f9ng n\u1ed5, \u0111\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n c\u1eadu \u1ea5y \u0111\u00f3ng vai tr\u00f2 h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng cho nh\u1eefng Griezmann, Mbappe hay Dembele c\u01a1 m\u00e0. H\u00e3y ch\u00fa \u00fd nh\u1eefng \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng chuy\u1ec1n s\u1eafc s\u1ea3o \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Pogba ph\u00e2n ph\u1ed1i v\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong s\u1ed1 \u0111\u00f3 \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00fap Ph\u00e1p m\u1edf t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 t\u1eeb th\u1ebf tr\u1eadn t\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u1ed1i kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n tr\u01b0\u1edbc Australia.\u201d<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">D\u00f9 sao th\u00ec \u0111\u1ea7u xu\u00f4i \u0111u\u00f4i l\u1ecdt, m\u00e0n ra qu\u00e2n v\u1edbi 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m tr\u1ecdn v\u1eb9n gi\u00fap Ph\u00e1p v\u1eefng tin h\u01a1n tr\u00ean ch\u1eb7ng \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng s\u1eafp t\u1edbi, v\u1edbi tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u1eaft l\u00e0 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng v\u1edbi v\u1ecb tr\u00ed s\u1ed1 m\u1ed9t. Th\u1ee9 n\u0103m n\u00e0y, th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Didier Deschamps s\u1ebd ch\u1ea1m tr\u00e1n Peru trong l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn th\u1ee9 hai b\u1ea3ng C World Cup 2018.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Thong so tran dau Phap 2-1 Australia\" title=\"Th\u00f4ng s\u1ed1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Ph\u00e1p 2-1 Australia\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/16/Phap-2--Australia.png\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Th\u00f4ng s\u1ed1 tr\u1eadn Ph\u00e1p 2-1 Australia</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Highlights tr\u1eadn Ph\u00e1p 2-1 Australia:<br>\r\n</strong></h2>\r\n<div class=\"mediaplayercontent\" data-href=\"https://video.bongda24h.vn/medias/MP4/2018/6/16/Phap-2-1-Australia.mp4\" data-width=\"480\" data-height=\"320\" data-type=\"m4v\"><img src=\"/Images/video-chi-tiet.jpg\" style=\"width: 300px; height:220px\" alt=\"\"></div>\r\n<strong>Gia Khoa (TTVN)</strong></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"235","checkdouble":"188659"},{"date":"21:47 16/06","title":"HLV Australia th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn thua Ph\u00e1p","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/6/16/hlv-australia-that-vong-truoc-tran-thua-phap.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>\u0110\u1ec3 thua ngay tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u m\u1edf m\u00e0n, r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng thuy\u1ec1n tr\u01b0\u1edfng c\u1ee7a Australia \u2013 HLV Van Marwijk t\u1ecf ra th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng khi c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 l\u00e0m n\u00ean chuy\u1ec7n tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0110T Ph\u00e1p.\r\n</h2><h2><br>\r\nNg\u01b0\u1eddi \u00dac nu\u1ed1i ti\u1ebfc sau th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">D\u00f9 b\u1ecb \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 th\u1ea5p h\u01a1n \u0110T Ph\u00e1p &ndash; m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng \u1ee9ng c\u1eed vi\u00ean h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u cho ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup, nh\u01b0ng Australia \u0111\u00e3 thi \u0111\u1ea5u ki\u00ean c\u01b0\u1eddng trong hi\u1ec7p 1. Th\u1eadm ch\u00ed, b\u00e0n thua \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd c\u0169ng b\u1eaft ngu\u1ed3n t\u1eeb t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng VAR, v\u1ed1n ch\u1ecbu nhi\u1ec1u tranh c\u00e3i.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ee9 s\u1edf chu\u1ed9t t\u00fai \u0111\u00e3 v\u00f9ng l\u00ean, v\u00e0 g\u1ea7n nh\u01b0 ngay l\u1eadp t\u1ee9c c\u00f3 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng g\u1ee1 h\u00f2a sau khi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Umtiti bi\u1ebfu cho qu\u1ea3 ph\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ec1n. Nh\u01b0ng trong nh\u1eefng ph\u00fat cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng, Paul Pogba \u0111\u00e3 ghi b\u00e0n th\u1eafng may m\u1eafn v\u00e0 \u1ea5n \u0111\u1ecbnh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng chung cu\u1ed9c cho G\u00e0 tr\u1ed1ng.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sau tr\u1eadn, HLV Bert van Marwijk chia s\u1ebb: &ldquo;T\u00f4i t\u1ef1 h\u00e0o v\u1ec1 c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh, nh\u01b0ng v\u1eabn c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y r\u1ea5t th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng. T\u00f4i ngh\u0129 ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n t\u1ed1t. R\u00f5 r\u00e0ng, kh\u00f4ng ai ch\u1edd \u0111\u1ee3i ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ch\u01a1i nh\u01b0 th\u1ebf n\u00e0y v\u1edbi \u0110T Ph\u00e1p.&rdquo;<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Van Marwijk t\u1ecf ra th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng cho c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2\" title=\"HLV Van Marwijk t\u1ecf ra th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng khi Australia thua Ph\u00e1p\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/16/hlv-australia-that-vong-truoc-tran-thua-phap.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>HLV Van Marwijk t\u1ecf ra th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng cho c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n&ldquo;C\u00f3 r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m trong tr\u1eadn, Ph\u00e1p th\u1eadm ch\u00ed c\u00f2n kh\u00f4ng bi\u1ebft ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0m g\u00ec, v\u00e0 t\u00f4i ngh\u0129 ch\u00fang t\u00f4i x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng l\u1eddi khen ng\u1ee3i. C\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u00e1p \u1ee9ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 95% y\u00eau c\u1ea7u m\u00e0 ban hu\u1ea5n luy\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ec1 ra, t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 n\u00e0o tr\u00e1ch h\u1ecd. \u00cdt nh\u1ea5t, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 h\u00f2a.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;Khi b\u1ea1n b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o m\u1ed9t gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u l\u1edbn nh\u01b0 th\u1ebf n\u00e0y, \u0111i\u1ec1u quan tr\u1ecdng l\u00e0 b\u1ea1n ph\u1ea3i gi\u1eef \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 t\u1ef1 tin xuy\u00ean su\u1ed1t. Kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 g\u00ec \u0111\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o, nh\u01b0ng ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb t\u1ed1t trong nh\u1eefng tu\u1ea7n qua. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n tinh th\u1ea7n chi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u1eaft, Australia s\u1ebd h\u01b0\u1edbng \u0111\u1ebfn tr\u1eadn chi\u1ebfn ti\u1ebfp theo v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 t\u1eadp trung cao \u0111\u1ed9.&rdquo;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">D\u00f9 HLV Van Marwijk t\u1ecf ra th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng v\u1edbi k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 n\u00e0y, nh\u01b0ng \u00f4ng kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ed5 l\u1ed7i cho h\u1ec7 th\u1ed1ng h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 video VAR &ndash; khi\u1ebfn Australia ch\u1ecbu b\u00e0n thua \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean. Chi\u1ebfn l\u01b0\u1ee3c gia ng\u01b0\u1eddi H\u00e0 Lan cho bi\u1ebft: &ldquo;Ch\u00fang ta kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 thay \u0111\u1ed5i \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3.&rdquo;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;M\u1ecdi ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1u n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 VAR, nh\u01b0ng v\u1edbi t\u00f4i, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 s\u1ef1 kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ea7u v\u00e0 ch\u00fang ta ph\u1ea3i h\u1ecdc c\u00e1ch l\u00e0m quen. D\u00f9 sao, t\u00f4i th\u00edch n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u h\u01a1n l\u00e0 c\u00f4ng ngh\u1ec7.&rdquo;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1edbi k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 n\u00e0y, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ee9 s\u1edf chu\u1ed9t t\u00fai s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u trong 2 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i. H\u1ecd s\u1ebd l\u1ea7n l\u01b0\u1ee3t ch\u1ea1m tr\u00e1n \u0110an M\u1ea1ch v\u00e0 Peru \u1edf 2 l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn ti\u1ebfp theo b\u1ea3ng C, World Cup 2018.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"mediaplayercontent\" data-href=\"https://video.bongda24h.vn/medias/MP4/2018/6/16/Phap-2-1-Australia.mp4\" data-width=\"480\" data-height=\"320\" data-type=\"m4v\"><img src=\"/Images/video-chi-tiet.jpg\" style=\"width: 300px; height:220px\" alt=\"\"></div>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/video/tong-hop-phap-21-australia-bang-c-world-cup-2018-461-188652.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/16/tong-hop-phap-21-australia-bang-c-world-cup-2018.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/video/tong-hop-phap-21-australia-bang-c-world-cup-2018-461-188652.html\">T\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p: Ph\u00e1p 2-1 Australia (B\u1ea3ng C World Cup 2018)</span><br>\r\nD\u00f9 g\u1eb7p nhi\u1ec1u kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n tr\u01b0\u1edbc Australia thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ea7y quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m, Les Bleus v\u1eabn c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng trong tr\u1eadn ra qu\u00e2n t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018. Pogba l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111em v\u1ec1 3...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/gianh-chien-thang-vat-va-griezmann-noi-gi-421-188656.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/16/gianh-chien-thang-vat-va-griezmann-noi-gi.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/gianh-chien-thang-vat-va-griezmann-noi-gi-421-188656.html\">Gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng v\u1ea5t v\u1ea3, Griezmann n\u00f3i g\u00ec</span><br>\r\nTh\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Dider Deschamps \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ea7u su\u00f4n s\u1ebb tr\u1eadn ra qu\u00e2n, v\u00e0 d\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng g\u00ec Griezmann ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u sau tr\u1eadn Ph\u00e1p 2-1 Australia.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nguy\u1ec7t Anh (TTVN)&nbsp;</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"234","checkdouble":"188660"},{"date":"17:56 16/06","title":"K\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 Ph\u00e1p vs Australia tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u b\u1ea3ng C World Cup 2018","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/15/ket-qua-phap-vs-australia-bang-c-hom-nay.png","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Chuy\u00ean trang Bongda24h c\u1eadp nh\u1eadt chi ti\u1ebft k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 Ph\u00e1p vs Australia tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u b\u1ea3ng C World Cup 2018 h\u00f4m nay. Th\u00f4ng tin k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3, t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1, ng\u01b0\u1eddi ghi b\u00e0n, di\u1ec5n bi\u1ebfn ch\u00ednh, tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Ph\u00e1p vs \u00dac b\u1ea3ng C World Cup 2018 17h00 chi\u1ec1u ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m nay 16/6.</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 hi\u1ec7p m\u1ed9t: Ph\u00e1p 0-0 Australia<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ghi b\u00e0n:<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">\u0110\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao h\u01a1n h\u1eb3n, kh\u00f4ng b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd v\u1edbi th\u1ebf tr\u1eadn \u00e1p \u0111\u1ea3o c\u1ee7a Ph\u00e1p ngay t\u1eeb ti\u1ebfng c\u00f2i khai cu\u1ed9c. Th\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ed3ng Kylian Mbappe, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb nh\u1ea5t tr\u00ean s\u00e2n, kh\u00f4ng ng\u1eebng t\u1ea3 xung h\u1eefu \u0111\u1ed9t v\u00e0 l\u00e0m kh\u1ed5 h\u00e0ng ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 Australia.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">M\u1eb7c d\u00f9 v\u1eady, ch\u00ednh \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n Ch\u00e2u \u00c1 m\u1edbi b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd s\u1edf h\u1eefu c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 nguy hi\u1ec3m \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean c\u1ee7a tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u. Ph\u00fat 17, Aaron Mooy c\u00f3 c\u00fa \u0111\u00e1 ph\u1ea1t kh\u00f3 ch\u1ecbu \u1edf b\u00ean c\u00e1nh tr\u00e1i, b\u00f3ng bay v\u1edbi qu\u1ef9 \u0111\u1ea1o ph\u1ee9c t\u1ea1p khi\u1ebfn Corento Tolisso l\u00f3ng ng\u00f3ng su\u00fdt ch\u00fat n\u1eefa ph\u1ea3n l\u01b0\u1edbi nh\u00e0. May m\u1eafn \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edfng Hugo Lloris \u0111\u1ed5 ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u1ee9u thua xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Sau t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng hi\u1ebfm hoi g\u00e2y th\u00f3t tim cho c\u00e1c nh\u00e0 \u0111\u01b0\u01a1ng kim \u00e1 qu\u00e2n Ch\u00e2u \u00c2u, Australia quay l\u1ea1i l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i co c\u1ee5m, nh\u01b0ng c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 d\u1ea7n d\u00e0 ch\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ed9ng h\u01a1n so v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng ph\u00fat \u0111\u1ea7u tr\u1eadn v\u00e0 s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng \u0103n mi\u1ebfng tr\u1ea3 mi\u1ebfng m\u1ed9t khi c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">D\u00f9 sao, Ph\u00e1p c\u0169ng mong ch\u1edd th\u1ebf tr\u1eadn n\u00e0y h\u01a1n h\u00f2ng d\u1ec5 \u0111\u00e1 h\u01a1n v\u00e0 ngay l\u1eadp t\u1ee9c, Lucas Hernandez c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m khi kho\u1ea3ng tr\u1ed1ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc khung th\u00e0nh c\u1ee7a Australia \u0111\u00e3 r\u1ed9ng m\u1edf. Tuy nhi\u00ean, h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 tr\u00e1i 22 tu\u1ed5i \u0111\u00e3 l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn nh\u1ed3i b\u00f3ng v\u00e0o trong cho Mbappe v\u00e0 b\u1ecb Milligan b\u1eaft b\u00e0i c\u1ea3n ph\u00e1.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">C\u1ee5c di\u1ec7n gi\u1eb1ng co nh\u01b0ng thi\u1ebfu h\u1ea5p d\u1eabn c\u1ee9 th\u1ebf k\u00e9o \u0111\u1ebfn cu\u1ed1i hi\u1ec7p m\u1ed9t, th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m Ph\u00e1p v\u00e0 Australia m\u1edbi ch\u1ecbu m\u1ea1o hi\u1ec3m h\u01a1n nh\u1eb1m ki\u1ebfm t\u00ecm l\u1ee3i th\u1ebf t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi v\u00e0o gi\u1edd ngh\u1ec9. Pogba chuy\u1ec1n d\u00e0i v\u01b0\u1ee3t tuy\u1ebfn cho Griezmann nh\u01b0 trung v\u1ec7 Sainsbury \u0111\u00e3 vung ch\u00e2n c\u1eaft b\u00f3ng k\u1ecbp th\u1eddi ngay \u1edf s\u00e1t r\u00eca v\u1ea1ch 5m50.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Ngay l\u1eadp t\u1ee9c, Australia c\u00f3 c\u00e2u tr\u1ea3 l\u1eddi v\u1edbi t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng ph\u1ed1i h\u1ee3p c\u00f3 n\u00e9t nh\u1ea5t tr\u1eadn. H\u1eadu v\u1ec7 tr\u00e1i Behich c\u00f3 tr\u1ed1ng tr\u1ea3i t\u1ea1t b\u00f3ng v\u00e0o trung l\u1ed9 nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecb c\u1ea3n ph\u00e1, run r\u1ee7i thay b\u1eadt l\u1ea1i \u0111\u00fang v\u1ecb tr\u00ed c\u1ee7a anh v\u00e0 tung c\u00fa s\u00fat xa nguy hi\u1ec3m theo b\u1ea3n n\u0103ng. \u0110\u00e1ng ti\u1ebfc khi b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e3 \u0111i cao h\u01a1n khung th\u00e0nh Lloris \u0111\u00f4i ch\u00fat.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Hi\u1ec7p m\u1ed9t k\u1ebft th\u00fac v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 h\u00f2a 0-0. \u0110\u00e2y r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng l\u00e0 k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 \u0111\u00e1ng th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng \u0111\u1ed1i v\u1edbi Ph\u00e1p, \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t nh\u1eefng ng\u00f4i sao l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t nh\u01b0ng thi \u0111\u1ea5u v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng m\u1edd nh\u1ea1t, t\u00f9 t\u00fang v\u00e0 b\u1ebf t\u1eafc nh\u01b0 Pogba v\u00e0 Griezmann.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh xu\u1ea5t ph\u00e1t thi \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u1eadn Ph\u00e1p vs Australia:<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"K\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 Ph\u00e1p vs Australia b\u1ea3ng C World Cup 2018 h\u00f4m nay 166 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"K\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 Ph\u00e1p vs Australia b\u1ea3ng C World Cup 2018 h\u00f4m nay 166 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/16/Ket-qua-Phap-vs-Australia-bang-C-World-Cup-2018-hom-nay-166-hinh-anh.png\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>\u0110\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh xu\u1ea5t ph\u00e1t tr\u1eadn Ph\u00e1p vs Australia</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><strong>Gia Khoa (TTVN)</strong></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"233","checkdouble":"188645"},{"date":"17:55 16/06","title":"TR\u1ef0C TI\u1ebeP Peru vs \u0110an M\u1ea1ch 23h00 ng\u00e0y 16/6 (World Cup 2018)","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/6/15/bong-da-peru-vs-dan-mach-bang-c.png","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp Peru vs \u0110an M\u1ea1ch: C\u1eadp nh\u1eadt li\u00ean t\u1ee5c di\u1ec5n bi\u1ebfn t\u01b0\u1eddng thu\u1eadt t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Peru vs \u0110an M\u1ea1ch b\u1ea3ng C World Cup 2018 l\u00fac 23h00 \u0111\u00eam ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m nay 16/6.</h2><h2>Tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp Peru vs \u0110an M\u1ea1ch: C\u1eadp nh\u1eadt li\u00ean t\u1ee5c di\u1ec5n bi\u1ebfn t\u01b0\u1eddng thu\u1eadt t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Peru vs \u0110an M\u1ea1ch b\u1ea3ng C World Cup 2018 l\u00fac 23h00 \u0111\u00eam ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m nay 16/6.</h2>\r\nKh\u00f4ng xem \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c, vui l\u00f2ng click v\u00e0o \u0111\u00e2y <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/truc-tiep-world-cup-2018/tran-dau/bong-da-peru-vs-dan-mach-bang-c-463-188649.html\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgb(128, 0, 0);\"><u><strong>TR\u1ef0C TI\u1ebeP PERU VS \u0110AN M\u1ea0CH</strong></u></span></span><br>\r\n<br></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"232","checkdouble":"188649"},{"date":"14:25 16/06","title":"Juan Mata v\u00e0 Fabregas c\u00f3 v\u00e0i l\u1eddi mu\u1ed1n g\u1eedi \u0111\u1ebfn David de Gea","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/16/juan-mata-co-vai-loi-muon-gui-den-david-de-gea.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Juan Mata ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 David de Gea, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1988 tin r\u1eb1ng th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh 28 tu\u1ed5i l\u00e0 th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi, De Gea s\u1ebd nhanh ch\u00f3ng ch\u1ee9ng t\u1ecf kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Mata tin De Gea s\u1ebd ch\u01a1i t\u1ed1t d\u1ea7n l\u00ean</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br />\r\nTrong tr\u1eadn h\u00f2a 3-3 gi\u1eefa T\u00e2y Ban Nha v\u00e0 B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha \u1edf b\u1ea3ng B World Cup 2018, th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n David de Gea \u0111\u00e3 m\u1eafc sai l\u1ea7m nghi\u00eam tr\u1ecdng. Ph\u00fat 44, t\u1eeb c\u00fa d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m t\u1eeb xa kh\u00f4ng qu\u00e1 kh\u00f3 c\u1ee7a Ronaldo, De Gea l\u1ea1i b\u1eaft tr\u01b0\u1ee3t b\u00f3ng bi\u1ebfu kh\u00f4ng cho B\u0110N m\u1ed9t b\u00e0n th\u1eafng.<br />\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Juan Mata ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 David de Gea sau sai l\u1ea7m tr\u01b0\u1edbc B\u0110N h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Juan Mata ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 David de Gea sau sai l\u1ea7m tr\u01b0\u1edbc B\u0110N h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/16/juan-mata-co-vai-loi-muon-gui-den-david-de-gea.jpg\" /></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Mata tin De Gea s\u1ebd ch\u01a1i t\u1ed1t trong th\u1eddi gian t\u1edbi</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br />\r\nRonaldo th\u1eadm ch\u00ed c\u00f2n b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd v\u1edbi t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng m\u1eafc sai l\u1ea7m r\u1ea5t nghi\u1ec7p d\u01b0 c\u1ee7a De Gea, m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n t\u1ec7 h\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a De Gea tr\u01b0\u1edbc B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha \u0111ang khi\u1ebfn anh g\u1eb7p ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eefng \u00e1p l\u1ef1c c\u1ef1c l\u1edbn.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br />\r\nKh\u00f4ng \u00edt nh\u1eefng \u00fd ki\u1ebfn cho r\u1eb1ng HLV TBN n\u00ean c\u00e2n nh\u1eafc \u0111\u1ec3 De Gea ng\u1ed3i d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb, b\u1edfi d\u01b0\u1eddng nh\u01b0 ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a Man \u0111\u1ecf \u0111ang g\u1eb7p v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 v\u1ec1 t\u00e2m l\u00fd.\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br />\r\nJuan Mata ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 David de Gea, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1988 tin r\u1eb1ng th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh 28 tu\u1ed5i l\u00e0 th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi, De Gea s\u1ebd nhanh ch\u00f3ng\u00a0ch\u1ee9ng t\u1ecf kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br />\r\n\u201cC\u1eadu \u1ea5y l\u00e0 th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi, th\u1eddi gian s\u1ebd tr\u1ea3 l\u1eddi cho \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3. T\u00f4i ngh\u0129 r\u1eb1ng De Gea s\u1ebd ch\u01a1i b\u00f9ng n\u1ed5 \u1edf nh\u1eefng tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u ti\u1ebfp theo, t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 \u0111ang ch\u1edd \u0111\u1ee3i c\u1eadu \u1ea5y s\u1eeda sai\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Fabregas c\u1ea3nh b\u00e1o De Gea</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u trong vai tr\u00f2 c\u1ee7a m\u1ed9t chuy\u00ean gia cho BBC, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Ces Fabregas n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 sai l\u1ea7m c\u1ee7a De Gea.<br />\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"TBN De Gea mac sai lam\" title=\"TBN De Gea mac sai lam\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/16/mourinho-noi-gi-ve-sai-lam-cua-david-de-gea.JPG\" /></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Fabregas kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n De Gea ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c m\u1eafc sai l\u1ea7m</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br />\r\n\u201cT\u00e0i n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a De Gea nh\u01b0 th\u1ebf n\u00e0o th\u00ec t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i n\u00f3i th\u00eam, c\u1eadu \u1ea5y x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o Top 3 th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi \u1edf th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i. Tuy nhi\u00ean, t\u00f4i v\u00e0 NHM T\u00e2y Ban Nha kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n nh\u00ecn th\u1ea5y nh\u1eefng sai l\u1ea7m m\u00e0 c\u1eadu \u1ea5y m\u1eafc ph\u1ea3i m\u1ed9t c\u00e1ch th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br />\r\nRio Ferdinand th\u00ec kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh: \u201cT\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng b\u00ean c\u1ea1nh De Gea, t\u00f4i bi\u1ebft r\u1eb1ng c\u1eadu \u1ea5y t\u00e0i n\u0103ng \u0111\u1ebfn m\u1ee9c n\u00e0o. T\u00f4i hy v\u1ecdng De Gea s\u1ebd ch\u01a1i t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n trong th\u1eddi gian t\u1edbi, ch\u1ec9 c\u1ea7n c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 t\u00e2m l\u00fd c\u1eadu \u1ea5y s\u1ebd c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ch\u1ee9ng t\u1ecf kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br />\r\n<span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/world-cup-2018/mourinho-noi-gi-ve-sai-lam-cua-david-de-gea-421-188619.html\" target=\"_blank\">Mourinho th\u00ec chia s\u1ebb</span>: \u201cNh\u1eefng sai l\u1ea7m s\u1ebd gi\u00fap De Gea tr\u01b0\u1edfng th\u00e0nh h\u01a1n, t\u00f4i tin c\u1eadu \u1ea5y s\u1ebd ch\u1ee9ng t\u1ecf n\u0103ng l\u1ef1c c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh \u1edf nh\u1eefng tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u ti\u1ebfp theo\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br />\r\nNguy\u1ec5n Huy\u1ec1n (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"231","checkdouble":"188632"},{"date":"14:46 16/06","title":"Chi ti\u1ebft h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng Alisson s\u1eafp k\u00fd v\u1edbi Real Madrid","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/3/29/chi-tiet-hop-dong-alisson-sap-ky-voi-real-madrid.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Real Madrid mua Alisson c\u1ee7a Roma th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng \u1edf H\u00e8 2018, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 th\u00f4ng tin \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Gianluca Di Marzio \u0111\u0103ng t\u1ea3i. Los Blancos \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ea3i b\u1ecf ra 52 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Brazil.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Real chuy\u1ec3n h\u01b0\u1edbng sang Alisson</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTrong nh\u1eefng m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Keylor Navas v\u1eabn duy tr\u00ec phong \u0111\u1ed9 kh\u00e1 t\u1ed1t, song n\u0103m nay c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 31 tu\u1ed5i, Los Blancos mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 m\u1ed9t th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n tr\u1ebb h\u01a1n.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Real Madrid mua Alisson th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 52 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Real Madrid mua Alisson th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 52 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/24/Real-Madrid-mua-Alisson-thanh-cong-voi-gia-52-trieu-bang-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Real mu\u1ed1n mua Alisson</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u00edch th\u00e2n ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch Perez x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn Real s\u1ebd mua th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p v\u00e0o H\u00e8 n\u00e0y. R\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau \u0111ang \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c h\u1ecd \u0111\u01b0a v\u00e0o t\u1ea7m ng\u1eafm, trong \u0111\u00f3 ph\u1ea3i k\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ebfn nh\u01b0 Courtois hay David de Gea.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nM\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, b\u00e1o ch\u00ed Anh \u0111\u01b0a tin, De Gea k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng 5 n\u0103m v\u1edbi MU, \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 bu\u1ed9c Real ph\u1ea3i chuy\u1ec3n h\u01b0\u1edbng sang nh\u1eefng m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau kh\u00e1c. \u0110\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Bernabeu \u0111\u00e3 chuy\u1ec3n h\u01b0\u1edbng sang th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Alisson c\u1ee7a Roma.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nM\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1992 \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i c\u1ef1c t\u1ed1t trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00f4 Italia, anh c\u0169ng \u0111ang l\u00e0 th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n s\u1ed1 1 c\u1ee7a \u0110T Brazil.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nRoma kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n b\u00e1n ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh, \u0111\u1ea5y l\u00e0 ch\u01b0a k\u1ec3 <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/nho-thuyet-khach-liverpool-sap-co-thu-mon-moi-172-187344.html\" target=\"_blank\">Liverpool c\u0169ng mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 Alisson</span>. Tuy nhi\u00ean, Real Madrid v\u1eabn t\u1ef1 tin v\u00e0o vi\u1ec7c chi\u00eau m\u1ed9\u00a0th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 26 tu\u1ed5i.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Real \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn mua Alisson</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Real Madrid mua Alisson c\u1ee7a Roma th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng \u1edf H\u00e8 2018, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 th\u00f4ng tin \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Gianluca Di Marzio cung c\u1ea5p. Los Blancos \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ea3i b\u1ecf ra 52 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Brazil.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Real Madrid mua Alisson th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 52 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" title=\"Real Madrid mua Alisson th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 52 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/11/Real-Madrid-mua-Alisson-thanh-cong-voi-gia-52-trieu-bang-hinh-anh-2.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Real \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n v\u1edbi Alisson\u00a0</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nC\u1ee5 th\u1ec3, Real \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n v\u1edbi Alisson, h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ed3ng \u00fd k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng 4 n\u0103m v\u1edbi c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Brazil, t\u1ea1i Bernabeu Alisson s\u1ebd h\u01b0\u1edfng l\u01b0\u01a1ng 250.000 b\u1ea3ng/tu\u1ea7n.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3 nh\u1eefng t\u01b0\u1edfng Real s\u1ebd c\u00f4ng b\u1ed1 t\u00e2n binh ng\u01b0\u1eddi Brazil tr\u01b0\u1edbc World Cup 2018, song v\u01b0\u1edbng m\u1eafc v\u1ec1 s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng khi\u1ebfn th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 th\u00f4ng qua.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTheo \u0111\u00f3, Real ch\u1ec9 ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi 44 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng trong khi Roma \u0111\u00f2i 70 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng. Sau m\u1ed9t th\u1eddi gian d\u00e0i \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n, Los Blancos \u0111\u00e3 thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a Italia nh\u1ea3 ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 52 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nReal s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i tr\u1ea3 \u0111\u1ee7 52 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng ti\u1ec1n chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng, h\u1ecd c\u00f2n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ph\u1ea3i tr\u1ea3 th\u00eam 8 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng ph\u1ee5 thu\u1ed9c v\u00e0o phong \u0111\u1ed9 c\u1ee7a ng\u00f4i sao 26 tu\u1ed5i.\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u01b0\u01a1ng Ng\u00e2n (TTVN)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"230","checkdouble":"188633"},{"date":"14:06 16/06","title":"Sao tr\u1ebb B\u00ecnh D\u01b0\u01a1ng b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd v\u00ec \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o danh s\u00e1ch tham d\u1ef1 ASIAD 2018","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/16/sao-tre-binh-duong-bat-ngo-vi-duoc-lot-vao-danh-sach-tham-du-asiad-2018.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp Argentina vs Iceland: C\u1eadp nh\u1eadt li\u00ean t\u1ee5c di\u1ec5n bi\u1ebfn t\u01b0\u1eddng thu\u1eadt t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Argentina vs Ai-x\u01a1-len b\u1ea3ng D World Cup 2018 l\u00fac 20h00 chi\u1ec1u ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m nay 16/6.</h2><h2>Tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp Argentina vs Iceland: C\u1eadp nh\u1eadt li\u00ean t\u1ee5c di\u1ec5n bi\u1ebfn t\u01b0\u1eddng thu\u1eadt t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Argentina vs Ai-x\u01a1-len b\u1ea3ng D World Cup 2018 l\u00fac 20h00 chi\u1ec1u ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m nay 16/6.</h2>\r\nB\u1ecb l\u1ed7i, vui l\u00f2ng click v\u00e0o \u0111\u00e2y <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/truc-tiep-world-cup-2018/tran-dau/argentina-vs-iceland-bang-d-463-188637.html\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgb(128, 0, 0);\"><u><strong>TR\u1ef0C TI\u1ebeP ARGENTINA VS ICELAND</strong></u></span></span><br></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"229","checkdouble":"188634"},{"date":"14:18 16/06","title":"Th\u00eam m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u2018h\u00e0ng th\u1ea3i\u2019 c\u1ee7a FLC Thanh H\u00f3a ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c c\u00f3 b\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed7 m\u1edbi","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/16/them-mot-cau-thu-hang-thai-cua-flc-thanh-hoa-chinh-thuc-co-ben-do-moi.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>M\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, BL\u0110 CLB SLNA \u0111\u00e3 x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn vi\u1ec7c c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u1eef k\u00fd c\u1ee7a ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Ho\u00e0ng V\u0103n B\u00ecnh cho giai \u0111o\u1ea1n l\u01b0\u1ee3t v\u1ec1 c\u1ee7a m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 2018 theo d\u1ea1ng cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n t\u1eeb FLC Thanh H\u00f3a.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Ho\u00e0ng V\u0103n B\u00ecnh c\u1ee7a FLC Thanh H\u00f3a ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c c\u00f3 b\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed7 m\u1edbi h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Ho\u00e0ng V\u0103n B\u00ecnh c\u1ee7a FLC Thanh H\u00f3a ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c c\u00f3 b\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed7 m\u1edbi h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/8/tien-ve-Hoang-Van-Binh-cua-FLC-Thanh-Hoa-chinh-thuc-co-ben-do-moi-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>Ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Ho\u00e0ng V\u0103n B\u00ecnh tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i kho\u00e1c \u00e1o CLB SLNA</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ho\u00e0ng V\u0103n B\u00ecnh l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong 3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 thu\u1ed9c di\u1ec7n thanh l\u00fd \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean d\u01b0\u1edbi th\u1eddi HLV Nguy\u1ec5n \u0110\u1ee9c Th\u1eafng t\u1ea1i FLC Thanh H\u00f3a. Sau khi BL\u0110 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00f4ng b\u00e1o v\u1ec1 chuy\u1ec7n n\u00e0y, V\u0103n B\u00ecnh \u0111\u00e3 t\u00edch c\u1ef1c t\u00ecm ki\u1ebfm b\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed7 m\u1edbi trong giai \u0111o\u1ea1n hai v\u00e0 anh nhanh ch\u00f3ng nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 ch\u00e0o \u0111\u00f3n c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng qu\u00ea h\u01b0\u01a1ng SLNA.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo th\u00f4ng tin m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t th\u00ec h\u00f4m qua (15/6), \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ee9 Ngh\u1ec7 \u0111\u00e3 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u1eef k\u00fd c\u1ee7a ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Ho\u00e0ng V\u0103n B\u00ecnh cho giai \u0111o\u1ea1n l\u01b0\u1ee3t v\u1ec1 c\u1ee7a m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 2018 theo d\u1ea1ng cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n t\u1eeb FLC Thanh H\u00f3a.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sinh n\u0103m 1989 t\u1ea1i Qu\u1ef3nh L\u01b0u, V\u0103n B\u00ecnh c\u00f9ng l\u1ee9a v\u1edbi Tr\u1ecdng Ho\u00e0ng, \u00c2u V\u0103n Ho\u00e0n,\u2026 - nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00e3 t\u1eebng l\u00ean \u0111\u1ed9i 1 SLNA t\u1eeb n\u0103m 2007... B\u1eb1ng n\u0103ng l\u1ef1c c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh, anh t\u1eebng kho\u00e1c \u00e1o \u0110T U20 Vi\u1ec7t Nam khi m\u1edbi 18 tu\u1ed5i.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">N\u0103m 2011, Ho\u00e0ng V\u0103n B\u00ecnh l\u00e0 th\u00e0nh vi\u00ean \u0110T U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam tham d\u1ef1 SEA Games. C\u0169ng trong qu\u00e3ng th\u1eddi gian thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u1edf SLNA, V\u0103n B\u00ecnh \u0111\u00e3 3 l\u1ea7n n\u00e2ng C\u00fap c\u00f9ng CLB (V.League 2011, C\u00fap QG 2010 v\u00e0 si\u00eau c\u00fap 2011).<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u00ec th\u1ebf, s\u1ef1 tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a V\u0103n B\u00ecnh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c xem l\u00e0 s\u1ef1 b\u1ed5 sung c\u1ea7n thi\u1ebft cho tuy\u1ebfn gi\u1eefa c\u1ee7a SLNA trong giai \u0111o\u1ea1n l\u01b0\u1ee3t v\u1ec1. L\u00fac n\u00e0y \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ee9 Ngh\u1ec7 \u0111ang ch\u1eadt v\u1eadt \u0111ua tr\u1ee5 h\u1ea1ng v\u1edbi Nam \u0110\u1ecbnh v\u00e0 S\u00e0i G\u00f2n, n\u00ean vi\u1ec7c c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 gi\u00fap s\u1ee9c c\u1ee7a V\u0103n B\u00ecnh s\u1ebd l\u00e0 t\u00edn hi\u1ec7u t\u1ed1t v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng.</p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/sao-tre-binh-duong-bat-ngo-vi-duoc-lot-vao-danh-sach-tham-du-asiad-2018-168-188634.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/16/sao-tre-binh-duong-bat-ngo-vi-duoc-lot-vao-danh-sach-tham-du-asiad-2018.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/sao-tre-binh-duong-bat-ngo-vi-duoc-lot-vao-danh-sach-tham-du-asiad-2018-168-188634.html\">Sao tr\u1ebb B\u00ecnh D\u01b0\u01a1ng b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd v\u00ec \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o danh s\u00e1ch tham d\u1ef1 ASIAD 2018</span><br>\r\nV\u1edbi phong \u0111\u1ed9 \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o CLB b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 B\u00ecnh D\u01b0\u01a1ng, h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 tr\u1ebb Nguy\u1ec5n Thanh Th\u1ea3o \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c HLV Park Hang Seo b\u1ed5 sung v\u00e0o danh s\u00e1ch s\u01a1 b\u1ed9 \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/sao-hagl-choi-xau-chinh-thuc-nhan-an-phat-nang-cua-vff-168-188628.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/15/sao-hagl-choi-xau-chinh-thuc-nhan-an-phat-nang-cua-vff.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/sao-hagl-choi-xau-chinh-thuc-nhan-an-phat-nang-cua-vff-168-188628.html\">Sao HAGL ch\u01a1i x\u1ea5u ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c nh\u1eadn \u00e1n ph\u1ea1t n\u1eb7ng c\u1ee7a VFF</span><br>\r\nM\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, Ban k\u1ef7 lu\u1eadt VFF \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f4ng b\u1ed1 c\u00e1c \u00e1n ph\u1ea1t cho c\u00e1c CLB sau v\u00f2ng 13 V-League, \u0111\u00e1ng ch\u00fa \u00fd h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 Nguy\u1ec5n V\u0103n H\u1ea1nh c\u1ee7a CLB HAGL b\u1ecb c\u1ea5m thi \u0111\u1ea5u 3 tr\u1eadn sau h\u00e0nh...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u00a0Minh Long (TTVN)<o:p></o:p></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"228","checkdouble":"188635"},{"date":"14:30 16/06","title":"Ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o V\u0103n Quy\u1ebft nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh, d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n tr\u1eadn Argentina vs Iceland","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/15/argentina-vs-iceland-bang-d.png","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Theo D\u00e2n Vi\u1ec7t, ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Nguy\u1ec5n V\u0103n Quy\u1ebft \u2013 ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111ang n\u1eafm t\u1ea5m b\u0103ng th\u1ee7 qu\u00e2n \u0110T Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u00e3 tin t\u01b0\u1edfng r\u1eb1ng Messi v\u00e0 c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng kh\u00f3 \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m \u1edf tr\u1eadn Argentina vs Iceland.</h2><h2>Ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o V\u0103n Quy\u1ebft nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n tr\u1eadn Argentina vs Iceland</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o V\u0103n Quy\u1ebft nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n tr\u1eadn Argentina vs Iceland h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o V\u0103n Quy\u1ebft nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n tr\u1eadn Argentina vs Iceland h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/12/Tien-dao-Van-Quyet-nhan-dinh-du-doan-tran-Argentina-vs-Iceland-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>V\u0103n Quy\u1ebft tin t\u01b0\u1edfng 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m s\u1ebd n\u1eb1m trong tay Argentina</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sau khi C.Ronaldo c\u00f3 m\u00e0n thi \u0111\u1ea5u ch\u00f3i s\u00e1ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0110T T\u00e2y Ban Nha v\u00e0o \u0111\u00eam qua, th\u00ec v\u00e0o t\u1ed1i nay 16/6, c\u00e1i t\u00ean \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng kh\u00f4ng k\u00e9m \u1edf World Cup l\u1ea7n n\u00e0y l\u00e0 si\u00eau sao Messi c\u0169ng s\u1ebd x\u1ecf gi\u00e0y ra s\u00e2n tham gia tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u gi\u1eefa Argentina vs Iceland.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f9ng \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p, kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Messi ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c ghi b\u00e0n l\u00e0 r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn. N\u00f3i v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y, ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Nguy\u1ec5n V\u0103n Quy\u1ebft c\u0169ng tin t\u01b0\u1edfng Messi v\u00e0 Argentina s\u1ebd c\u00f3 tr\u1ecdn v\u1eb9n 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean t\u1ea1i gi\u1ea3i.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;&ldquo;World Cup 2014 \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea1i nhi\u1ec1u ti\u1ebfc nu\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ed1i v\u1edbi Messi c\u00f9ng Argentina khi thua \u0110\u1ee9c \u1edf tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft. T\u1ea1i World Cup 2018, nhi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao Brazil, \u0110\u1ee9c, Ph\u00e1p&nbsp;nh\u01b0 nh\u1eefng \u1ee9ng vi\u00ean h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u cho danh hi\u1ec7u v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch. Nh\u01b0ng c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n t\u00f4i v\u1eabn tin \u1edf tu\u1ed5i 31, M10 s\u1ebd ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u1ea5u \u1ea5n nh\u01b0 m\u1ed9t huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i trong k\u1ef3 World Cup c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 coi l\u00e0 cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng trong s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">S\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 g\u00ec ng\u1ea1c nhi\u00ean n\u1ebfu Argentina l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng. Trong khi \u0111\u00f3, Iceland kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n c\u00e1ch n\u00e0o kh\u00e1c l\u00e0 ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c trung th\u00e0nh v\u1edbi l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i k\u1ef7 lu\u1eadt, ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 ch\u1eb7t, ch\u1edd c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u01b0a ra nh\u1eefng \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng ph\u1ea3n c\u00f4ng nhanh v\u1edbi vai tr\u00f2 &quot;nh\u1ea1c tr\u01b0\u1edfng&quot; c\u1ee7a&nbsp;Gylfi Sigurdsson - c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111ang kho\u00e1c \u00e1o Everton t\u1ea1i gi\u1ea3i Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u1ea1i Euro 2016, Iceland t\u1eebng khi\u1ebfn c\u1ea3 ch\u00e2u \u00c2u v\u00e0 th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd khi \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i tuy\u1ec3n Anh \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ecdt t\u1edbi t\u1eadn t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft. V\u00e0 ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn Argentina c\u0169ng c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i ch\u01a1i r\u1ea5t t\u1eadp trung n\u1ebfu mu\u1ed1n gi\u00e0nh k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t&rdquo;, V\u0103n Quy\u1ebft nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/truc-tiep-world-cup-2018/tran-dau/argentina-vs-iceland-bang-d-463-188637.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/15/argentina-vs-iceland-bang-d.png\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/truc-tiep-world-cup-2018/tran-dau/argentina-vs-iceland-bang-d-463-188637.html\">TR\u1ef0C TI\u1ebeP Argentina vs Iceland 20h00 ng\u00e0y 16/6 (World Cup 2018)</span><br>\r\nTr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp Argentina vs Iceland: C\u1eadp nh\u1eadt li\u00ean t\u1ee5c di\u1ec5n bi\u1ebfn t\u01b0\u1eddng thu\u1eadt t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Argentina vs Ai-x\u01a1-len b\u1ea3ng D World Cup 2018 l\u00fac...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">M\u1eb7c d\u00f9 v\u1eady, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111ang ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng cho CLB H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i v\u1eabn tin t\u01b0\u1edfng v\u00e0o m\u1ed9t chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c c\u1ee7a nh\u00e0 \u00e1 qu\u00e2n World Cup 2014. Anh n\u00f3i th\u00eam: &ldquo;Argentina nh\u1ec9nh h\u01a1n h\u1eb3n so v\u1edbi Iceland v\u1ed1n l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea7u d\u1ef1 World Cup c\u1ea3 v\u1ec1 l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u00e0 kinh nghi\u1ec7m. Tuy nhi\u00ean, trong b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 kh\u00f3 n\u00f3i tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111i\u1ec1u g\u00ec. N\u1ebfu t\u1ea1o \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ed9t b\u1ea7u kh\u00f4ng kh\u00ed v\u00e0 th\u1ebf tr\u1eadn t\u1ed1t,&nbsp;t\u00f4i tin Argentina s\u1ebd th\u1eafng v\u1edbi c\u00e1ch bi\u1ec7t 2 b\u00e0n v\u00e0 Messi s\u1ebd l\u1eadp c\u00f4ng&rdquo;.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Cu\u1ed9c \u0111\u1ecd s\u1ee9c gi\u1eefa <span href=\"Argentina vs Iceland\" target=\"_blank\">Argentina vs Iceland</span> s\u1ebd di\u1ec5n ra v\u00e0o l\u00fac 20h00 t\u1ed1i nay tr\u00ean VTV6 v\u00e0 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Bongda24h c\u1eadp nh\u1eadt tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp di\u1ec5n bi\u1ebfn tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u. Mong b\u1ea1n \u0111\u1ecdc ch\u00fa \u00fd \u0111\u00f3n xem.</p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/nhan-dinh-argentina-vs-iceland-20h00-ngay-166-giai-ma-hien-tuong-421-188591.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/15/nhan-dinh-argentina-vs-iceland-20h00-ngay-166-giai-ma-hien-tuong.png\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/nhan-dinh-argentina-vs-iceland-20h00-ngay-166-giai-ma-hien-tuong-421-188591.html\">Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Argentina vs Iceland (20h00 ng\u00e0y 16/6): Gi\u1ea3i m\u00e3 hi\u1ec7n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng</span><br>\r\nTrong tr\u1eadn ra qu\u00e2n c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh, hi\u1ec3n nhi\u00ean Leo Messi v\u00e0 c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh tr\u00f2 c\u01b0\u1eddi. D\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Argentina vs Iceland b\u1ea3ng D World Cup...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nMinh Long (TTVN)<o:p></o:p></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"227","checkdouble":"188636"}]}